## Implementation Steps

1. Create client/info.rs
2. Implement render_connected() notification
3. Implement render_disconnected() notification
4. Implement render_detail() for full info
5. Add capabilities formatting
6. Implement plain-text fallbacks
7. Test with various client info

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Connection notification shows client name/version
- [ ] Disconnection notification includes reason if provided
- [ ] Detail view shows all client properties
- [ ] Capabilities are formatted clearly
- [ ] Plain-text fallback works correctly
- [ ] Handles missing optional fields gracefully

